This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it focuses on using unsupervised learning for efficient exploration in reinforcement learning. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with developing algorithms for intelligent agents. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it deals with reinforcement learning in the context of control systems and robotics. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it deals with learning from rich observations.
